creator: Star_Developer
descriptionHtml:
- Keeping track of the score of a American football game by Tapping on the
points buttons to add points to each team.
- You can add each Team name.
- You can select the period or round of the game by using period button :
by tapping on it increase by one.
by long click on it reset it back to round 1.
- You can use Timer :
by Tapping on clock to start Timer.
pause button to pause timer.
continue button to continue timer.
stop button to stop game.
- After stopping the game you can get time lost by using time lost button.
- Finally you can reset score or reset time or both by using Reset Score button and Reset Timer button.

* The app contains American football Scoreboard and can be updated
with other sports.
